Gabriely, G.; Yi, M.; Narayan, R. S.; Niers, J. M.; Wurdinger, T.; Imitola, J.; Ligon, K. L.; Kesari, S.; et al. (2011). "Human Glioma Growth Is Controlled by MicroRNA-10b". Cancer Research. 71 (10): 3563–72. PMC 3096675 . PMID 21471404. doi:10.1158/0008-5472.CAN-10-3568. 
Boldin, M. P.; Taganov, K. D.; Rao, D. S.; Yang, L.; Zhao, J. L.; Kalwani, M.; Garcia-Flores, Y.; Luong, M.; et al. (2011). "miR-146a is a significant brake on autoimmunity, myeloproliferation, and cancer in mice". Journal of Experimental Medicine. 208 (6): 1189–1201. PMC 3173243 . PMID 21555486. doi:10.1084/jem.20101823. 
Park, Jong-Kook; Henry, Jon C.; Jiang, Jinmai; Esau, Christine; Gusev, Yuriy; Lerner, Megan R.; Postier, Russell G.; Brackett, Daniel J.; Schmittgen, Thomas D. (2011). "miR-132 and miR-212 are increased in pancreatic cancer and target the retinoblastoma tumor suppressor". Biochemical and Biophysical Research Communications. 406 (4): 518–23. PMC 3069485 . PMID 21329664. doi:10.1016/j.bbrc.2011.02.065. 
Thum, Thomas; Chau, Nelson; Bhat, Balkrishen; Gupta, Shashi Kumar; Linsley, Peter S.; Bauersachs, Johann; Engelhardt, Stefan (2011). "Comparison of different miR-21 inhibitor chemistries in a cardiac disease model". Journal of Clinical Investigation. 121 (2): 461–2. PMC 3026747 . PMID 21285516. doi:10.1172/JCI45938. 
Chau, B. Nelson; Brenner, David A. (2011). "What goes up must come down: The emerging role of microRNA in fibrosis". Hepatology. 53 (1): 4–6. PMID 21254156. doi:10.1002/hep.24071. 





 
