	Manufacture and Commercialization of Collaboration Compounds Developed under such Program and to obtain the licenses described in Section 5.2 under the terms and conditions set forth in this Agreement (each, a 

	Program
	Option

	), which right is exercisable, at GSKs sole discretion in accordance with the procedures set forth below, (a) at the [...***...] Stage (

	[...***...]Option

	), (b) if GSK does not exercise its Candidate
	Selection Option for a Program, upon Completion of the PoC Trial (the 

