	Regulus Collaboration Technology, as it may be developed or identified to which GSK has a right or license under this Agreement that is necessary or useful for GSK to further Develop, Manufacture, Commercialize or otherwise exploit the progression
	of Collaboration Compounds into Licensed Product(s) as permitted under this Agreement.





