	[...***...] for such Program, then GSK shall pay Regulus milestones at [...***...] set forth above; and




	(c) after
	[...***...] for such Program, but prior to the [...***...], then GSK shall pay Regulus milestones at [...***...] set forth above.





	6.5.4 

