	take into consideration the comments of the other Party for all matters relating to interferences, reissues, re-examinations and oppositions with respect to those Patent Rights in which such other Party has an ownership interest, is licensed or
	sublicensed thereunder or may in the future, in accordance with this Agreement, obtain a license or sublicense thereunder.





