	such terminated Program(s) be deemed Refused Candidates, nor shall any Licensed Products containing any such Collaboration Compound(s) as an active ingredient(s) be deemed Refused Candidate Products, to which Regulus would otherwise
	have rights under Section 4.2.7 of this Agreement;




	(c) GSK shall be obligated to pay Regulus milestones as set
	forth in Section 6.5.3 and royalties as set forth in Section 6.6.1(d) (subject to Section 6.6.2), in each case depending on the stage of Development at which the termination occurred;




